{"word":"ἐτήσιος","slug":"ἐτήσιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐτήσιος</b></el> <el>(ἐτήσιος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἔτος'><el>ἔτος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>lasting a year, a year long</i>, <el>πένθος</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>every year, annual</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}